l-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/police-recommend-closing-case-against-yeshiva-head-who-said-all-gazans-should-be-killed/00000190-27d9-d95e-a3ff-effdb62c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列讨论新的西岸定居点以及对巴勒斯坦权力机构的制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-discusses-new-west-bank-settlements-sanctions-against-palestinian-authority/00000190-27bf-d14b-a999-27ffd8830000</link><description>安全内阁考虑对拉马拉在国际论坛上针对以色列的法律运动采取惩罚措施。斯莫特里奇推动定居点建设，以回应其他国家承认巴勒斯坦国</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:07:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-discusses-new-west-bank-settlements-sanctions-against-palestinian-authority/00000190-27bf-d14b-a999-27ffd8830000</guid></item><item><title>美国高级特使：以色列与真主党的战争可能导致伊朗大规模袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/top-u-s-envoy-israeli-war-with-hezbollah-could-lead-to-wide-scale-iranian-attack/00000190-27c4-d66b-abfd-7fe6eb620000</link><description>阿莫斯·霍赫斯坦周一在与包括总理内塔尼亚胡和国防部长在内的一系列以色列官员会面时发出了警告</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 21:49:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/top-u-s-envoy-israeli-war-with-hezbollah-could-lead-to-wide-scale-iranian-attack/00000190-27c4-d66b-abfd-7fe6eb620000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战事中，内塔尼亚胡与以色列将军之间的激烈战争愈演愈烈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/amid-the-fighting-in-gaza-the-war-between-netanyahu-and-israels-generals-is-intensifying/00000190-279c-d5f5-a5d6-effe367b0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡和以色列国防军之间在加沙战争问题上的分歧变得如此严重，以至于内塔尼亚胡阵营现在指责军队将军们采用了法西斯政党所青睐的经典“背后捅刀子”阴谋论。但这是一种冒险的策略，甚至是危险的策略</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 19:48:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/amid-the-fighting-in-gaza-the-war-between-netanyahu-and-israels-generals-is-intensifying/00000190-279c-d5f5-a5d6-effe367b0000</guid></item><item><title>数万名以色列人发起一周反对政府的抗议活动：“我们不会放弃”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/tens-of-thousands-of-israelis-launch-week-of-protests-against-government-wont-give-up/00000190-275b-d340-a1f8-2f5fc20c0000</link><description>抗议者呼吁举行选举、加沙停火和释放人质协议，并谴责哈雷迪征兵豁免</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 19:40:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/tens-of-thousands-of-israelis-launch-week-of-protests-against-government-wont-give-up/00000190-275b-d340-a1f8-2f5fc20c0000</guid></item><item><title>本格维尔警察如何威胁以色列的新闻自由</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-17/ty-article/.highlight/how-ben-gvirs-police-threaten-press-freedom-in-israel/00000190-26ca-d66b-abfd-7fee84ea0000</link><description>在报道抗议活动时，我会把记者证挂在脖子上，希望骑警不会因为骑车碾压记者而感到头疼。但随着政府削弱以色列的新闻自由，我开始怀疑它是否很快会让我成为目标</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 19:09:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-17/ty-article/.highlight/how-ben-gvirs-police-threaten-press-freedom-in-israel/00000190-26ca-d66b-abfd-7fee84ea0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们国家上空的一个大而美丽的铁穹”：特朗普将以色列导弹防御系统引入美国的幻想</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/inside-trumps-fantasy-to-bring-israels-iron-dome-missile-defense-system-to-america/00000190-266a-d14b-a999-27eb35f10000</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普在竞选过程中反复告诉共和党人，如果当选，他将建造美国铁穹——尽管该系统可能只有在美国受到加拿大或墨西哥攻击时才有效</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 18:35:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/inside-trumps-fantasy-to-bring-israels-iron-dome-missile-defense-system-to-america/00000190-266a-d14b-a999-27eb35f10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方计划展示加沙的成功，向公众展示它击败了哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-plans-to-showcase-gaza-successes-to-show-public-it-has-beaten-hamas/00000190-275d-d66b-abfd-7fff71fa0000</link><description>国防机构的消息人士称，哈马斯在拉法的最后几个营正处于被击败的边缘，政府尚未向军方通报此后发生的情况</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 18:27:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-plans-to-showcase-gaza-successes-to-show-public-it-has-beaten-hamas/00000190-275d-d66b-abfd-7fff71fa0000</guid></item><item><title>“可憎”：大学校长猛烈抨击学生会法案，要求解雇“煽动反对以色列”的教师</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/abomination-hebrew-university-president-slams-bill-pushed-by-national-student-union/00000190-2705-d14b-a999-27ed677c0000</link><description>该法案将迫使大学立即解雇任何发表被认为否定以色列作为犹太民主国家存在的观点的教员</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 17:38:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/abomination-hebrew-university-president-slams-bill-pushed-by-national-student-union/00000190-2705-d14b-a999-27ed677c0000</guid></item><item><title>一个依良心拒服兵役者对以色列人和巴勒斯坦人从河流到海洋的生活的愿景</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-refusniks-vision-of-life-for-israelis-and-palestinians-from-the-river-to-the-sea/00000190-2688-d14b-a999-27e9f5770000</link><description>索菲亚·奥尔 (Sofia Orr) 因拒绝加入以色列国防军而刚刚在军事监狱里度过了 85 天。这位 19 岁的女孩在被认定为良心拒服兵役者后获释，她讲述了自己这样做的原因、左翼和右翼极端分子的袭击，以及她从狱友那里听到的消息</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 17:33:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-refusniks-vision-of-life-for-israelis-and-palestinians-from-the-river-to-the-sea/00000190-2688-d14b-a999-27e9f5770000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡随身携带一本关于古希腊民主衰落的书。我们应该读多少内容？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-carries-book-on-the-fall-of-greek-democracy-how-much-should-we-read-into-it/00000190-25f4-de0a-af9b-fdffa92d0000</link><description>最近几天，内塔尼亚胡一定要在《雅典的兴衰》中拍照，该片聚焦于雅典领导人中普遍存在的道德败坏，并导致了雅典的垮台。内塔尼亚胡很可能不会内化这些教训</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 17:29:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-carries-book-on-the-fall-of-greek-democracy-how-much-should-we-read-into-it/00000190-25f4-de0a-af9b-fdffa92d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 255 天：消息人士称，如果没有“后天”计划，以色列国防军在拉法取得的成果就被浪费了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-255-idf-gains-in-rafah-wasted-without-day-after-plan-source-says/00000190-2702-d14b-a999-27eb76150000</link><description>甘茨辞职后，内塔尼亚胡总理解散战争内阁 ■ 接近内塔尼亚胡的消息人士表示，有关战争的敏感决定仍将在排除极右翼部长的有限论坛上做出 ■ 拜登的中东特使阿莫斯·霍赫斯坦在前往黎巴嫩之前在以色列与以色列高级官员会面试图缓和以色列和真主党之间的紧张局势 ■ 这是战争进入 255 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 16:37:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-255-idf-gains-in-rafah-wasted-without-day-after-plan-source-says/00000190-2702-d14b-a999-27eb76150000</guid></item><item><title>联合国小组称缺乏数据来确定加沙北部是否存在饥荒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/un-panel-says-data-lacking-to-determine-whether-famine-exists-in-northern-gaza/00000190-269a-d2de-af9e-67fa68040000</link><description>联合国专家小组反驳了人权组织的调查结果，但警告不要利用该报告来否认“加沙地带目前无疑正在遭受极端的人类苦难”</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 15:46:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/un-panel-says-data-lacking-to-determine-whether-famine-exists-in-northern-gaza/00000190-269a-d2de-af9e-67fa68040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列面临着相信与真主党的战争不可避免的危险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/could-this-talmudic-concept-help-avert-an-inevitable-israel-hezbollah-war/00000190-25da-d95e-a3ff-edfe95270000</link><description>你知道 ipcha Mistabra 是什么吗？你应该——以色列的军事和政治领导人现在就应该考虑黎巴嫩可能爆发的全面战争</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 15:43:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/could-this-talmudic-concept-help-avert-an-inevitable-israel-hezbollah-war/00000190-25da-d95e-a3ff-edfe95270000</guid></item><item><title>马尔代夫正在审查因排除巴勒斯坦人问题而全面禁止以色列人的提议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/asia-and-australia/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/maldives-reviewing-proposed-blanket-ban-on-israelis-over-issue-of-palestinians-exclusion/00000190-2673-d5f5-a5d6-effb15270000</link><description>司法部长艾哈迈德·乌沙姆表示，该禁令也将影响持有以色列护照的巴勒斯坦人，这是“一些人非常关心的问题”</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 15:37:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/asia-and-australia/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/maldives-reviewing-proposed-blanket-ban-on-israelis-over-issue-of-palestinians-exclusion/00000190-2673-d5f5-a5d6-effb15270000</guid></item><item><title>极端正统派部长关于军队豁免：“我们赢得了选举，难道我们不能做出决定吗？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-minister-on-idf-exemption-we-won-the-election-dont-we-get-to-decide/00000190-2518-d3e6-a191-773bcbb90000</link><description>建设和住房部长声称国防机构对征召极端正统犹太人不感兴趣；以色列国防军司令哈勒维：征召正统派显然是必要的，每个营都将减轻数千名预备役人员的负担</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 14:31:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-minister-on-idf-exemption-we-won-the-election-dont-we-get-to-decide/00000190-2518-d3e6-a191-773bcbb90000</guid></item><item><title>作为阿拉伯以色列人在朝觐期间访问麦加，我的身份让加沙最大的支持者感到困惑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/visiting-mecca-as-a-palestinian-israeli-my-identity-confused-gazas-biggest-supporters/00000190-25cc-d2de-af9e-65ee12ef0000</link><description>陪同朝觐者前往麦加朝觐的《国土报》记者 Deiaa Haj Yahia 会见了一些信徒，他们不知道以色列有穆斯林阿拉伯公民，其他人则谴责“犹太复国主义政权”，与加沙巴勒斯坦人和担心与以色列关系正常化的沙特人深表声援。以色列可能“损害我们在穆斯林世界的地位”</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 13:21:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/visiting-mecca-as-a-palestinian-israeli-my-identity-confused-gazas-biggest-supporters/00000190-25cc-d2de-af9e-65ee12ef0000</guid></item><item><title>2023年以色列国防出口额达到创纪录的131亿美元；超过三分之一是防空交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/israel-defense-exports-hit-record-13-billion-in-2023-over-a-third-are-air-defense-deals/00000190-25d7-d5f5-a5d6-edffd8630000</link><description>报告称，近五年来，以色列国防出口规模翻了一番，近三年出口额记录每年都被打破</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 12:41:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/israel-defense-exports-hit-record-13-billion-in-2023-over-a-third-are-air-defense-deals/00000190-25d7-d5f5-a5d6-edffd8630000</guid></item></channel></rss>